{
  "title": "Ellipse",
  "description": "Mutable axis-aligned ellipse shape defined by a centre position and separate horizontal (`rx`) and vertical (`ry`) half-radii. Implements ShapeLike for use in the intersection pipeline. `collidesWith` supports: SceneNode (AABB), Rectangle, Circle, Polygon, and Ellipse. Ellipse-vs-Line always returns `null` — use `intersectsWith`.",
